    "- Website: Professional, benefit-driven, data-backed. Lead with customer outcomes.",
    "- Social media (LinkedIn, Twitter): Conversational, industry-aware. Share insights, not promotions.",
    "- Blog: Educational, thought-leadership. Position RavenStack team members as experts in AI collaboration.",
    "- Support communications: Empathetic, solution-oriented. Acknowledge the problem before presenting the fix.",
    "- Sales materials: Consultative, data-driven. Use customer metrics and competitive comparisons.",
    "- Internal communications: Direct, data-informed. No jargon, no spin.",
    "",
    "## Visual Identity",
    "",
    "### Logo",
    "- Primary: Raven icon + 'RavenStack' wordmark (horizontal layout)",
    "- Alternate: Raven icon only (minimum 32px width)",
