    "- Clear space: 1x icon height on all sides (nothing should intrude into this space)",
    "- Never stretch, rotate, recolor, add shadows, or add outlines to the logo",
    "- Never place the logo on busy or low-contrast backgrounds",
    "",
    "### Brand Colors",
    "- RavenStack Blue: #2563EB (primary — buttons, links, headers)",
