    "",
    "### Iconography",
    "- Lucide icon library for product interfaces (consistent with Nimbus UI design system)",
    "- Simple line icons for marketing materials",
    "- Do not mix icon styles (do not use filled icons alongside outline icons)",
    "",
    "## Content Guidelines",
    "",
    "### Numbers and Data",
