    "- NimbusApp has no lower entry point — it is $99 or nothing",
    "- RavenStack has 40 features vs NimbusApp's approximately 15",
    "- NimbusApp cannot serve non-engineering teams (no Budget Tracker, Stakeholder Map, Portfolio View, Client Portal)",
    "- Our 168 Basic accounts demonstrate the land-and-expand motion working at scale",
    "",
    "## Objection 2: 'AcmeSaaS has better AI features'",
