    "- Acknowledge that AcmeSaaS's AI is GA — do not dismiss this fact",
    "- Pivot to quality and breadth: we have 5 AI features vs their single AI assistant",
    "- Share our GA timeline to demonstrate commitment",
    "- Reference our error rates to show quality trajectory",
