    "- AI Search: 492 uses, 5.5% error rate — launching GA January 15, 2026",
    "- AI Summary: 356 uses, 4.5% error rate — GA February 2026",
    "- AI Agent Builder: 367 uses, 4.9% error rate — GA March 2026",
    "- AcmeAI reported error rate: approximately 6% (from G2 reviews and industry analysis)",
    "- RavenStack Enterprise: $199/seat vs AcmeSaaS Enterprise: $279/seat (40% premium)",
    "",
